languages.text: “不过亲爱的大人，您还活着。这种暂时的不便您想必可以忍受，直到您抵达您的家族领地为止，是吧？”
languages.original_text: "But my dear sir, you are alive. Surely such temporary inconveniences can be tolerated until you have reached your family demesne?"
